          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The 252Cf source was purchased from Isotope Products,",
                "Inc. (source No. A4-818). The overall size of the",
                "capsule is approximately 1-cm in diameter and 0.5-cm",
                "thick with a 0.25-mm thick beryllium foil window on",
                "one side and a backing of 0.127-cm thick stainless",
                "steel on the other side. The 252Cf source activity as",
                "of March 2002 was nominally 50 mu-Ci. The 252Cf",
                "activity is embedded in an anodized aluminum disk and",
                "sealed in the capsule. In the 2-nd ref. the gamma-ray",
                "yields were measured also with an older source of",
                "252Cf made in 1991 and mounted in the same type",
                "capsule."
              ]
            }
          ],
